(207, 'Totals - Custom', 'report', 3, 50, 30, 'modules/bms/report/invoices_totals.php', 'Creater your own custom invoice totaling report, specify groupings, totals, averages and whether to display summary, invoice, and invoice detail information.', 1, '2009-04-13 10:46:43', 2, '2022-06-02 17:59:40'),
